snippet.title: Amber Heard FLOPS On Her First Days of Filming Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
The first day of filming of the new DC Extended Universe movie franchise Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom was expected to be huge news to its fans, but rather it clothed to be an enormous flop. Why? Well, everyone watched its first movie, and it was indeed a blockbuster hit. However, after the chaotic downfall between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s marriage intensified, many former fans of the DCEU film have turned their backs on Amber Heard. And following the countless petitions of supporters for Warner Brothers to alleviate Amber from her role as Queen Mera, which had not been granted, many supporters have turned their backs on the entire movie franchise also . So how did the fans react when finally, the primary day of filming of Aquaman 2 had been announced? Well, let’s determine during this video.
